column3: An entity that is part of a contractual interaction and has decision making abilities or has obligations and responsibilities
The human individual or person involved as the First Party in the contractual interaction
The Service Provider involved as the Second Party in the contractual interaction
A party other than First and Second Party in the contractual interaction
A legal authority that is empowered to investigate and determine compliance
An agent that represents a party and can act on behalf of it - such as for signing contracts or negotiating terms
column9: Agents can be human or non-human i.e. machine agents

column3: The party that is responsible for a specific activity
An agent that represents a party and can act on behalf of it to make decisions regarding privacy (and related matters)
column9: Privacy Agents can be human or non-human i.e. machine agents

column3: A Privacy Agent that represents the Person or First Party
A Privacy Agent that repersents the Service Provider or Second Party
